style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)<\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\\\"><h3><span style=\\\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\"> \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span>Discipleship<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><h2 style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">We are committed to spiritual, mental and social development of our people.(Luke 2:52; Ephesians 4:11-13)<\\/h2><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\\\"><h3>Pentecostal Heritage<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\"> \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 15px;\\\">We are committed to seeing the person and the power of the Holy Spirit in all we do. (Mark 15:15-17; Acts 1:8; Acts 2:4)<\\/span><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\\\"><h3><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span>Sound Doctrine<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">We are committed to proclaiming and practicing the whole counsel of God as found in the Holy Bible wit integrity and accuracy (Luke 24:19; Acts 1:1; Timothy 3:16; Acts 20:20)<\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\\\"><h3><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 <\\/span>Excellence<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><h3 style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">We are committed to seeing excellence exhibited in all our endeavors upholding the beauty of God (2 Corinthians 8:7; Daniel 5:12; 1 Corinthians 14:40)<\\/h3><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\\\"><h3>Integrity<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">We are committed to transparency and honesty in all our personal, public and corporate affairs. (Daniel 6:3-4; Romans 14:16; 2 Thessalonians 5:21-22)<\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\\\"><h3><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span>Accountability<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">\\u00a0We are committed to building Structures and practices that will enhance accountability with the understanding that God shall require us to give an account (Romans 12:14)<\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\\\"><h3><span style=\\\"font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span>Organizational Structure<\\/h3><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\\\">The operation of the work and ministry of the PAOZ is carried out through its structures.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]');
