:4-5)<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a3a3a; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Discipleship<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a3a3a; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Pentecostal Heritage<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">We are committed to seeing the person and the power of the Holy Spirit in all we do. (Mark 15:15-17; Acts 1:8; Acts 2:4)<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #161616;\\\">Sound Doctrine<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">We are committed to proclaiming and practicing the whole counsel of God as found in the Holy Bible wit integrity and accuracy (Luke 24:19; Acts 1:1; Timothy 3:16; Acts 20:20)<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001p