\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Discipleship<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Pentecostal Heritage<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to seeing the person and the power of the Holy Spirit in all we do. (Mark 15:15-17; Acts 1:8; Acts 2:4)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Sound Doctrine<\\/span><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to proclaiming and practicing the whole counsel of God as found in the Holy Bible wit integrity and accuracy (Luke 24:19; Acts 1:1; Timothy 3:16; Acts 20:20)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Excellence<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to seeing excellence exhibited in all our endeavors upholding the beauty of God (2 Corinthians 8:7; Daniel 5:12; 1 Corinthians 14:40)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Integrity<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to transparency and honesty in all our personal, public and corporate affairs. (Daniel 6:3-4; Romans 14:16; 2 Thessalonians 5:21-22)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\">Accountability<\\/span><\\/b><b><\\/b><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">We are committed to building Structures and practices that will enhance accountability with the understanding that God shall require us to give an account (Romans 12:14)<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 14.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 0in; border: 1pt none windowtext;\\\"><b>Organizational Structure<br \\/><\\/b><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 20px;\\\">The operation of the work and ministry of the PAOZ is carried out through its structures.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]');
