e: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)</p><ul><li style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">        Discipleship</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">We are committed to spiritual, mental and social development of our people.(Luke 2:52; Ephesians 4:11-13)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">Pentecostal Heritage</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">      We are committed to seeing the person and the power of the Holy Spirit in all we do. (Mark 15:15-17; Acts 1:8; Acts 2:4)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">         Sound Doctrine</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">We are committed to proclaiming and practicing the whole counsel of God as found in the Holy Bible wit integrity and accuracy (Luke 24:19; Acts 1:1; Timothy 3:16; Acts 20:20)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">       Excellence</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">We are committed to seeing excellence exhibited in all our endeavors upholding the beauty of God (2 Corinthians 8:7; Daniel 5:12; 1 Corinthians 14:40)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">   Integrity</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">We are committed to transparency and honesty in all our personal, public and corporate affairs. (Daniel 6:3-4; Romans 14:16; 2 Thessalonians 5:21-22)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">      Accountability</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\"> We are committed to building Structures and practices that will enhance accountability with the understanding that God shall require us to give an account (Romans 12:14)</p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;\">     Organizational Structure</li></ul><p style=\"font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: left;\">The operation of the work and ministry of the PAOZ is carried out through its structures.</p>		\n			<h2>Values</h2>		\n		<p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->a.       <!--[endif]-->People</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to loving people and sharing the gospel of Jesus Christ at every opportunity.(John 3:16)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->b.      <!--[endif]-->Fellowship</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to creating an environment where believers can relate to one another with genuine love and acceptance (Ephesians 2:20-22; Romans 12:4-5)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->c.       <!--[endif]-->Discipleship</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to spiritual, mental and social development of our people.(Luke 2:52; Ephesians 4:11-13)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">Pentecostal Heritage</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->d.      <!--[endif]-->We are committed to seeing the person and the power of the Holy Spirit in all we do. (Mark 15:15-17; Acts 1:8; Acts 2:4)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->e.      <!--[endif]-->Sound Doctrine</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to proclaiming and practicing the whole counsel of God as found in the Holy Bible wit integrity and accuracy (Luke 24:19; Acts 1:1; Timothy 3:16; Acts 20:20)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->f.        <!--[endif]-->Excellence</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to seeing excellence exhibited in all our endeavors upholding the beauty of God (2 Corinthians 8:7; Daniel 5:12; 1 Corinthians 14:40)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->g.       <!--[endif]-->Integrity</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to transparency and honesty in all our personal, public and corporate affairs. (Daniel 6:3-4; Romans 14:16; 2 Thessalonians 5:21-22)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]-->h.      <!--[endif]-->Accountability</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto;\">We are committed to building Structures and practices that will enhance accountability with the understanding that God shall require us to give an account (Romans 12:14)</p><p style=\"marg