ound-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b>Integrity</b><b></b></p><p>We are committed to transparency and honesty in all our personal, public and corporate affairs. (Daniel 6:3-4; Romans 14:16; 2 Thessalonians 5:21-22)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b>Accountability</b><b></b></p><p>We are committed to building Structures and practices that will enhance accountability with the understanding that God shall require us to give an account (Romans 12:14)</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b>Organizational Structure<br /></b>The operation of the work and ministry of the PAOZ is carried out through its structures.</p><p>History</p><p>Six Pillars</p>','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','88-revision-v1','','','2021-10-27 09:50:44','2021-10-27 09:50:44','',88,'http://paozupperroom.local/?p=330',0,'revision','',0);
